      <guid>https://cookmaker.cn/project/gaussianimate/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;GaussiAnimate is a scaffold-skin rigging system for reconstructing and animating diverse categories from 4D Gaussian or mesh sequences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It introduces the skelebone representation and Partwise Motion Matching for controllable yet expressive reanimation. The project page includes the paper, teaser, method overview, and extensive qualitative results.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
